1. Moje *lične* stvari su u ormaru. (My personal items are in the closet.)
2. Upravo radim na *ličnom* razvoju. (I'm currently working on personal development.)
3. *Lični* kontakti su mi važni u poslu. (Personal contacts are important to me in business.)
4. Ona je vrlo *lična* u svojim razgovorima. (She is very personal in her conversations.)
5. *Lično* smatram da je ova odluka pogrešna. (Personally, I think this decision is wrong.)
6. Naše *lične* informacije treba čuvati u tajnosti. (Our personal information should be kept confidential.)
7. On je izgubio *ličnu* kartu i sada mu je potrebna nova. (He lost his ID card and now he needs a new one.)
8. U ovom projektu moramo dati *lični* doprinos. (In this project, we need to make a personal contribution.)
9. Ukoliko imate neke *lične* probleme, možete se obratiti psihologu. (If you have any personal problems, you can consult a psychologist.)
10. *Lični* automobili su izvor zagađenja vazduha. (Personal cars are a source of air pollution.)